SUMMARY:Visit the Easter Bunny + KIDZ BOP Bunny Dance Parties
DESCRIPTION:The Easter Bunny is back at Washington Square starting on March 6th! Visit the Bunny in the Summit Court! You may visit the Easter Bunny for free\, but to take photos with the Easter Bunny you must pay for a Photo Package. \nYou can also Hop into the fun at our KIDZ BOP Bunny Dance Parties! Every hour on the hour\, kids can dance along with Bunny to upbeat KIDZ BOP hits and easy-to-follow moves. \nThe Bunny’s Schedule:\n\nMarch 6 – 8:\n\nFriday: 2PM – 7PM\nSaturday: 10AM – 8PM\nSunday: 11AM – 6PM\n\nMarch 9 – 21:\n\nMonday-Thursday: 2PM – 7PM\nFriday:  11AM – 7PM\nSaturday:  10AM – 8PM\nSunday: 11AM – 7PM\n\nMarch 22 – April 4:\n\nSunday – Friday:  11AM – 7PM\nSaturday:  10AM – 8PM
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/kidz-bop-bunny-dance-parties-easter-bunny-photos/
LOCATION:Washington Square Mall\, 9585 SW Washington Square Rd\, Portland\, OR. 97223\, Portland\, OR\, 97223\, United States
CATEGORIES:Easter,Indoor,Kids Calendar
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/bunny-dance-parties-at-washington-square.jpg
GEO:45.4502551;-122.7813094
