SUMMARY:St. Patrick's Day Celebration at McMenamins Kennedy School
DESCRIPTION:The leprechauns are on our side this year – pubs and restaurants will be serving McMenamins own Irish Stout alongside food and drink specials! May the luck of the Irish be with us all. Sláinte!
