SUMMARY:85th Annual St. Patrick's Day Celebration
DESCRIPTION:Tuesday\, March 17th\, 2026 4-7pm \nFAMILY FRIENDLY! Pipe band\, dancers\, live music\, face painting\, musical petting zoo\, hot and cold food\, tea and coffee\, beer and wine! \nSchedule \n\nDoors 3:30 pm\nTVF&R Pipes and Drums Band 4:15 pm\nChildren’s Area 4:00 – 6:30 pm\n\nCornhole Toss\nFace Painters\nStorytelling\nDrawing\n\n\nBand – Mikey Belgan Trio 4:45 – 6:15 pm\nOregon Irish Dance Academy – Finale 6:15 pm\n\nTickets \n\n$12 – Adults online (ages 21+)\n$15 – Adults door (ages 21+)\n$7 – Youth online (ages 12-20)\n$10 – Youth door (ages 12-20)Youth ages 11 and under are admitted FREE with paying adults\n\nOnline ticket prices rise to the door price at 4 pm on March 16.  \nAll ages \nEditor’s note: This event is a community submission.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/85th-annual-st-patricks-day-celebration/
LOCATION:Aquinas Hall\, 340 NE Clackmas St\, Portland\, OR\, 97232\, United States
CATEGORIES:Festival,Kids Calendar,Music,St. Patrick's
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://pdxparent.com/wp-content/uploads/MG_0749-scaled.jpeg
ORGANIZER;CN="All-Ireland Cultural Society":MAILTO:irishclubpdx@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
