SUMMARY:Free Parking Day at Metro Parks
DESCRIPTION:Get out and explore nature in 2026! Enjoy free parking at Oxbow and Blue Lake regional parks\, Broughton Beach\, M. James Gleason Memorial Boat Ramp and Chinook Landing Marine Park on 19 days in 2026. \nThe dates for 2026 free parking days are: \n\nJan.1\, 15 and 19\nFeb. 16 and 19\nMarch 19\nApril 16\nMay 21\nJune 18 and 19\nJuly 16\nAug. 20\nSept. 17\nOct. 12 and 15\nNov. 11\, 19 and 27\nDec. 17\n\nParking at all other Metro parks and boat ramps is free year-round.
URL:https://pdxparent.com/event-single/free-parking-day-at-metro-parks/2026-03-19/
LOCATION:OR
CATEGORIES:Active,Family Fun,Kids Calendar,Outdoor,Plants & Nature
